Hi Folks, <br>
<br>
Just some extra info regarding the new drum quest, hope it'll help someone looking for it.<br>
<br>
You need to get a Star of Odus (found in Erudin library or Cabilis) and give it to male banker in FV to get a 6<br>
slots box.<br>
<br>
There are 6 coins to gather, as everyone should know by now.<br>
<br>
The foraged coin isn't food, you cannot consume it, so don't worry about it.<br>
<br>
The coin in Dalnir isn't dropped from The Kly, not even The Kly Overseer, it's from The Kly Incepacitor<br>
 (spelling?) up on second floor (Kly and Overseer is third floor). You should be ok to get that mob with 2 people - and if you're really good at fear kiting (and know exactly where you're going in Dalnir - invised), should be ok to pull it solo and kill it yourself.<br>
<br>
The coin in Kaesora need at least 3 people to be safe, cuz there are LOTS of high greeners and when they<br>
 gang up, it's actually pretty tough. The failed crype raider is right inside the library and it spawn pretty fast, like 30 minutes or so.<br>
<br>
The Captain of the Guards in City of Mist spawns near the left side of the platform after the first bridge and<br>
gate, (usually a skeleton spawn there), took it a while to spawn, but shouldn't be hard to kill.<br>
<br>
 The rest of the coins are pretty easy to get, Bloodgill in lake and Scorpikis Scourager in the scorpikis valley in Overthere (one of them pops right in front of me when I get down there!)<br>
<br>
Combine all coins in the 6 slot box (make sure you ID it before combining!) to get a NO DROP item called Full Box of Coins (or something like that), give that to the male high elf banker (forgot his name) and get your new drum =)<br>
<br>
 This is the testing results of the drums :<br>
<br>
                            Guardian Rythem : <br>
                            No Drum : 30 sv magic (0% bonus)<br>
                            Reg Hand Drum : 54 sv magic (80% bonus)<br>
                            MM Drum : 63 sv magic (110% bonus)<br>
                            New Drum (Tombarine) : 66 sv magic (120% bonus)<br>
<br>
 And since it's the only drum that is NO DROP and gives stats bonus (+5 INT), I like it a lot<br>
<br>
